    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter regarding your advertisement in yesterday newspaper dated 13-June-2022 for the post of clerk in your post office. I have decided to apply for this job because i have all skills which are required for this vacancy.",
        "I am commerce graduate and completed a certificate course in Modern Financial Accountancy. As, I have experience of two years in same field and got appreciation certificate while performing my duty in Multinational Company. Moreover, i am good in handling office tasks, best in accountancy and have good knowledge about internet and MS-office.",
